description:
In an interview taped backstage at the Newport Jazz Festival, guitarist John Scofield talks about Hudson, the jazz supergroup featuring Scofield on guitar, John Medeski on keyboards, Larry Grenadier on bass and Jack DeJohnette on drums.

This interview was taped backstage at the 2017 Newport Jazz Festival, where Scofield performed with Hudson.  For more information about Scofield, visit www.johnscofield.com 

Interview by Irene Lee. Produced for JazzTimes by Lee Mergner. You can find more videos, plus news, features, reviews and lots more at www.jazztimes.com
